  "release_notes": [
    "Add Adaptive Approval Graph tables for approval instances, rounds, nodes, edges, and events.",
    "Keep workflow_tasks and the existing psa_timesheet_action RPC as the production execution path while graph tables act as a synchronized read model.",
    "Add non-blocking synchronization triggers from timesheets and workflow_tasks into the graph model.",
